tapeline - Dual License
=======================

This project uses two licenses, which is the normal split for open hardware:

1. HARDWARE & DOCUMENTATION  ->  CERN-OHL-P v2 (Permissive)
   Applies to: the Verilog RTL under rtl/ and the design docs under docs/.

2. SOFTWARE & TOOLING  ->  MIT (see LICENSE-MIT)
   Applies to: the golden model and tooling under sim/, the host helpers under
   host/, the Makefile, and CI scripts.

